repair.repairedDockerfile:
# DOCKER-VERSION 1.2.0
#FROM node:argon
#FROM node:17
FROM public.ecr.aws/bitnami/node:17
# Bundle app source
COPY . /rtdb
WORKDIR /rtdb
# Install app dependencies
RUN npm install && npm cache clean --force;

EXPOSE 9001
CMD ["npm", "start"]
